00:00:00.430 --> 00:00:02.860
Agar siz buyurtma shakliga juda ko‘p 
elementlarni qo‘shishni boshlasangiz, 

00:00:02.860 --> 00:00:05.370
unda pastki qismidagi matn 
ko‘rinmay qo‘lishi mumkin.

00:00:05.370 --> 00:00:07.030
Ushbu matn ekrandan chetga 
chiqib ketishi mumkin, 

00:00:07.030 --> 00:00:08.680
shu sababli uni ko‘ra olmaysiz.

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:11.610
Vertikal chiziqli ko‘rinish, 
agar u ekranning chetidan tashqarida bo‘lsa,

00:00:11.610 --> 00:00:13.420
u siljimaydi vertikal yo‘nalish bo‘ylab.

00:00:13.420 --> 00:00:16.309
Vertikal ravishda harakatlantirish 
uchun ilovangizga biron bir aniq element 

00:00:16.309 --> 00:00:17.620
qo‘shishingiz kerak.

00:00:17.620 --> 00:00:21.610
Buni yaxshi misol deb hisoblamiman, 
lekin men asosan maketimizdagi ko‘rinishlardan 

00:00:21.610 --> 00:00:24.650
nusxa ko‘chirdim va keyin 
ularni bir birining ustiga qo‘ydim.

00:00:24.650 --> 00:00:27.210
Ko‘rishingiz mumkinki, 
ushbu ekranning chekkasida 

00:00:27.210 --> 00:00:29.650
ko‘proq matn mavjud bo‘lsa ham,
u hali ham harakatlanmaydi.

00:00:30.820 --> 00:00:35.578
Bu, ayniqsa, telefoningizni gorizontal
holatga o‘tkazganda va ekran 

00:00:35.578 --> 00:00:39.444
portret rejimiga qaraganda qisqaroq bo‘lsa, 
keng tarqalgan muammodir.

00:00:39.444 --> 00:00:41.630
Agar harakatlanishi mumkin bo‘lganda,
juda qulay bo‘lar edi.

00:00:42.980 --> 00:00:45.720
Endi ushbu muammoga yechim 
topishni sizga qoldiraman.

00:00:45.720 --> 00:00:48.290
Tugatganingizdan so‘ng, bu yerda buni 
qanday qilganingizni tushuntirib otsangiz bo‘ladi.

00:00:48.290 --> 00:00:51.160
Siz uni qalamingiz bilan yozishingiz 
yoki shunchaki klaviaturangizdan foydalanishingiz mumkin.

